    {
        "content": "<p>Ok so there are multiple thing that goes wrong:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The <code>{i : ℕ}</code> parameter shouldn't appear in the statement</li>\n<li><code>simp</code> is the load-bearing part that does all the hard work for you. It invokes <code>Set.countable_iUnion_iff</code> which is what you wanted to avoid</li>\n</ul>",
        "id": 561298047,
        "sender_full_name": "Weiyi Wang",
        "timestamp": 1764633704
