        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"816344\">Aaron Liu</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/Countable.20Union.20of.20Countable.20Sets.20is.20Countable/near/561298696\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>you seem to have proven by induction that the finite union of countable sets is countable</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Ah, that resolves what <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"133339\">@Mirek Olšák</span> said. I guess I'm not proving it for a countably infinite number of sets. I see!</p>",
